metrics.visualTitle: Carte des Etiquette DPE dans le 69

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		FILTER(
			KEEPFILTERS(
				SUMMARIZE(
					SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
						'logement'[Adresse_(BAN)],
						'dpe'[Etiquette_DPE],
						"CountRowslogement", COUNTROWS('logement'),
						"CountRowsdpe", COUNTROWS('dpe')
					),
					'logement'[Adresse_(BAN)],
					'dpe'[Etiquette_DPE]
				)
			),
			NOT(
				('logement'[Adresse_(BAN)], 'dpe'[Etiquette_DPE]) IN {("99 MontÃ e de la Grande CÃ te 69001 Lyon", "G"),
					("Lyon", "E"),
					("Lyon", "D"),
					("Beauvallon", "A"),
					("Saint-Vérand", "A"),
					("Saint-Étienne-la-Varenne", "A"),
					("Albigny-sur-Sa*u00f4ne", "A"),
					("Meys", "A"),
					("Saint-Genis-les-Ollières", "A"),
					("Ternay", "A"),
					("Rue du Bocage Fleuri 69124 Colombier-Saugnieu", "A"),
					("Rue Jean Collet 69330 Meyzieu", "A"),
					("Francheville", "A"),
					("Saint-Lager", "A"),
					("Saint-Pierre-de-Chandieu", "A"),
					("Savigny", "A"),
					("Beaujeu", "A"),
					("Charly", "A"),
					("Craponne", "A")}
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(
				FILTER(
					KEEPFILTERS(
						SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
							'logement'[Adresse_(BAN)],
							'dpe'[Etiquette_DPE],
							__DS0FilterTable,
							"MinCode_postal__BAN_", IGNORE(
								CALCULATE(MIN('logement'[Code_postal_(BAN)]))
							),
							"CountRowslogement", COUNTROWS('logement'),
							"CountRowsdpe", COUNTROWS('dpe')
						)
					),
					OR(
						NOT(ISBLANK('logement'[Adresse_(BAN)])),
						NOT(ISBLANK('dpe'[Etiquette_DPE]))
					)
				)
			),
			"'logement'[Adresse_(BAN)]", 'logement'[Adresse_(BAN)],
			"'dpe'[Etiquette_DPE]", 'dpe'[Etiquette_DPE],
			"MinCode_postal__BAN_", [MinCode_postal__BAN_]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'logement'[Adresse_(BAN)])

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'dpe'[Etiquette_DPE])

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

	VAR __DS0PrimaryCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0PrimaryBase))

	VAR __DS0SecondaryCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0SecondaryBase))

	VAR __DS0SpaceCount = (__DS0PrimaryCount * __DS0SecondaryCount)

	VAR __DS0SparseFactor = MIN(5, DIVIDE(__DS0SpaceCount, __DS0IntersectionCount))

	VAR __DS0TargetIntersectionCount = CEILING(3500 * __DS0SparseFactor, 1)

	VAR __DS0InitTargetPrimaryCount = 
		IF(
			__DS0IntersectionCount <= 3500,
			IF(
				__DS0SpaceCount <= __DS0TargetIntersectionCount,
				3500,
				FLOOR(
					SQRT(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount * DIVIDE(__DS0PrimaryCount, __DS0SecondaryCount)),
					1
				)
			),
			IF(
				AND(__DS0PrimaryCount > 800, __DS0SecondaryCount > 60),
				CEILING(DIVIDE(__DS0TargetIntersectionCount, 60), 1),
				IF(
					__DS0SecondaryCount > 60,
					__DS0PrimaryCount,
